<i>to see if there's a little dip
in their brightness.</i>

02:08.961 --> 02:13.592
<i>That dip could indicate
a planet passing by as it orbits the star.</i>

02:13.675 --> 02:17.763
<i>We can follow up with other telescopes
that look for a little wobble in the light</i>

02:17.846 --> 02:20.224
