02:20.307 --> 02:21.725
<i>When we do find a planet,</i>

02:21.808 --> 02:28.732
<i>we use very powerful space telescopes,
like Hubble or the James Webb Telescope,</i>

02:28.815 --> 02:30.901
<i>to examine the planet more closely,</i>

02:30.984 --> 02:33.654
<i>to see if it might be able
to support life.</i>

02:35.614 --> 02:38.659
